channel.title: Trying to get client online through hamachi
channel.description:
No flames, im only using it because no-ip doesn't work for me.
I'm using it until i get donations, but if someone could show me what is wrong and why i can't go online via teamview, i would love the help. Nobody has been able to figure it out yet.
Please, no links, i have used the search bar, only help.
